description: Luna, a 4.46-billion-year-old male PlanetHuman moon, orbits Earth.  He's physically unique, lacking a nose, ears, neck, and cheeks, with light grey skin, meteor holes, and cartoony features.  Kind and quiet, he secretly loves his friend Titan and is dedicated to helping Earth despite feeling unappreciated.  His personality is optimistic yet prone to anger when frustrated.  The description includes details about his genitals.
